data.text:
Located in Central, Hong Kong, Bidding Street is one of the busiest commercial streets, with dense shops and pedestrians, and it will not be deserted until the middle of the night. Many famous buildings are on this street, such as Landmark Plaza, Global Building, etc., and the historic Biddinghang Building, which is a landmark building after the opening of Hong Kong. Bida Street is also a collection of internationally renowned brand goods, especially some luxury manufacturers here to support the field, showing the gold benefits of this place.

Bida Street and Heyao Road and Canton Road are similar, traditional commercial streets, shopping malls, there are many high-end office buildings and hotels here, there are several well-known shopping malls, and there are some international big-name specialty stores.

The street is not very long in Central, but he gathers Hong Kong's famous commercial buildings, such as Taikoo Plaza, Yihe Building, etc., all around it, so the world's first-tier luxury brands have specialty stores there.
